Package me.kinomoto.proteam.history

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    History
    History class store the nodes of actions that may be repeated or deleted by using Back and Forward options from the menu.
    HistoryNodeAbstract
    The class is the abstract prototype for creating HistoryNodes for actions in the Surroundings
    HistoryNodeDeleteElement
    The class is creating a HistoryNode after deleting element from the working plain
    HistoryNodeDeleteSource
    The class is creating a HistoryNode after deleting BeamSource from the working plain
    HistoryNodeMirror
    The class is creating a HistoryNode after changing parameters of the Mirror
    HistoryNodeMoveAbstract
    The class is the abstract prototype for creating HistoryNodes for translations in the Surroundings
    HistoryNodeMoveElement
    The class is creating a HistoryNode after translating optical element on the working plain
    HistoryNodeMoveSource
    The class is creating a HistoryNode after translating BeamSource on the working plain
    HistoryNodeNewElement
    The class is creating a HistoryNode after creating new optical element on the working plain
    HistoryNodeNewSource
    The class is creating a HistoryNode after new BeamSource on the working plain
    HistoryNodePrism
    The class is creating a HistoryNode after changing parameters of the Prism
    HistoryNodeRotationAbstract
    The class is the abstract prototype for creating HistoryNodes for rotations in the Surroundings
    HistoryNodeRotationElement
    The class is creating a HistoryNode after rotating optical element on the working plain
    HistoryNodeRotationSource
    The class is creating a HistoryNode after rotating BeamSource on the working plain
    HistoryNodeSource
    The class is creating a HistoryNode after changing parameters of the BeamSource
    HistoryNodeSurroundings
    The class is creating a HistoryNode after changing parameters of the Surroundings
